PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FNursery teachers in some of England's
OL,7,Fmost deprived communities can apply
OL,8,Ffor #4,500 cash bonuses under a new
OL,9,Fgovernment plan to drive recruitment
OL,10,Fin early years education.
OL,12,FIt comes as the sector has been
OL,13,Fcalling for more funding and support
OL,14,Ffor years to tackle a "crisis" in
OL,15,Fstaff employment and retention, with
OL,16,Flow pay remaining one of the biggest
OL,17,Fissues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FThe payment incentive, which was
OL,7,Fannounced by the Department for
OL,8,FEducation (DfE) last July and launched
OL,9,Fon Tuesday, is open to staff holding
OL,10,Fqualified teacher status, early years
OL,11,Fteacher status or early years
OL,12,Fprofessional status.
OL,14,FWhile some within the early years
OL,15,Fsector have welcomed Tuesday's
OL,16,Fannouncement, others argue the plans
OL,17,Fdo not go far enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FNeil Leitch, CEO of Early Years
OL,7,FAlliance, told ITV News: "One person
OL,8,Fcoming into an early years setting is
OL,9,Fnot going to do it. What we need to do
OL,10,Fis invest in the entire workforce.
OL,12,F"I mean we have a recruitment and
OL,13,Fretention crisis which frankly we've
OL,14,Fnever witnessed before and it's
OL,15,Fbecause people are leaving because
OL,16,Fit's not financially sustainable to
OL,17,Foperate in these areas."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FThe areas across England that have
OL,7,Fbeen selected for the government's
OL,8,Fscheme are based on deprivation,
OL,9,Fteacher shortages and school readiness
OL,10,Flevels, the DfE said.
OL,12,FThe first wave of incentives will be
OL,13,Foffered in ten areas: Sandwell,
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough, Tameside, Rochdale,
OL,15,FBolton, Hartlepool, Rotherham, Dudley,
OL,16,FLuton, and Barking and Dagenham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FIt will be expanded to a further 20
OL,7,Fareas later this year, and teachers
OL,8,Fcan apply via an online claims
OL,9,Fservice, with eligible nurseries set
OL,10,Fto receive a link from the DfE.
OL,12,FFinding affordable and available
OL,13,Fnursery places is often a huge
OL,14,Fstruggle for many parents.
OL,16,FAn ITV News report previously revealed
OL,17,Fan estimated 1.5 million children in
OL,18,Fthe UK are thought to be living in a
OL,19,Fchildcare desert, where there are more
OL,20,Fthan three children for every
OL,21,Favailable nursery place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FWaiting lists for nursery places are
OL,7,Foften so long that some parents are
OL,8,Funder pressure to sign their children
OL,9,Fup before they're even born, while the
OL,10,Fothers grapple with the rising costs
OL,11,Fof early years care.
OL,13,FHannah Jones, an insurance manager who
OL,14,Fhas two young children, said childcare
OL,15,Fwas something that "weighed on my
OL,16,Fmind" as a working parent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FShe recalled being advised to start
OL,7,Flooking for a nursery place just weeks
OL,8,Fafter giving birth to her daughter
OL,9,FLily, who is now five, which added an
OL,10,F"extra layer of pressure".
OL,12,F"I had never had a baby before and
OL,13,Fwhen you've got people saying 'you
OL,14,Fneed to think about nursery' already,
OL,15,FI was just trying to think about being
OL,16,Fa mum," she told ITV News.
OL,18,F"I knew I was going to be going back
OL,19,Fto work, so to then have that as an
OL,20,Fextra layer of worry, it wasn't very
OL,21,Fnice to be honest."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FMrs Jones's youngest child, Teddy, who
OL,7,Fis two, attends nursery in Salford,
OL,8,Fwhich is one of the areas in the North
OL,9,FWest that will be included in the
OL,10,Fexpanded government strategy later
OL,11,Fthis year.
OL,13,FHer husband, Oliver Jones, is a train
OL,14,Fdriver and said having a trusted
OL,15,Fchildcare setting close is the "most
OL,16,Fimportant thing" but there are
OL,17,Ffinancial costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,F"We don't have immediate family around
OL,7,Fthat we could depend on, so we need
OL,8,Fsomething where we know the set days
OL,9,Fthat they're in nursery," he told ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,F"I guess it's just a fact of modern
OL,13,Flife that you know it's going to be
OL,14,Fexpensive and you have to make
OL,15,Fsacrifices elsewhere to pay for this,
OL,16,Fbut it's just one of those things that
OL,17,Fneeds paying for."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FAs working parents, the couple said
OL,7,Fthey had to consider whether them both
OL,8,Freturning to work was "financially
OL,9,Fviable", despite both wanting to.
OL,11,FThe government has said its aim with
OL,12,Fthe bonuses is to help nurseries
OL,13,Fattract and keep more qualified staff
OL,14,Fso "they can deliver the funded
OL,15,Fchildcare that saves families up to
OL,16,F#8,000 a year in the communities that
OL,17,Fneed it most".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,F"I enjoy working as much as I enjoy
OL,7,Fbeing a mum," Mrs Jones said. "But you
OL,8,Fjust have to think about, paying all
OL,9,Fthis money, are we actually going to
OL,10,Fbe better off and is it worth doing?
OL,12,F"It's just a shame when you're
OL,13,Fenjoying your job role and there's a
OL,14,Fpossibility you may have to leave
OL,15,Fbecause of the cost of (childcare)
OL,16,Fessentially," she added.
OL,18,FYears of underfunding means nurseries
OL,19,Fand early years settings are feeling
OL,20,Fthe pressure, with many in the
OL,21,Fworkforce choosing to leave the sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FThis has a knock-on effect for
OL,7,Fchildren, with evidence showing those
OL,8,Fin more disadvantaged communities are
OL,9,Fhit the hardest.
OL,11,FJust 58% of children in the most
OL,12,Fdeprived areas reach the desired level
OL,13,Fof development by the end of
OL,14,Freception, compared to 77% in the
OL,15,Fleast deprived areas, according to
OL,16,Fgovernment data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fhas promised a consultation will
OL,8,Ffollow on how to raise the status and
OL,9,Frecognition of early years teachers
OL,10,Fand address current differences in pay
OL,11,Fcompared with schools.
OL,13,FCurrently fewer than one in 10 nursery
OL,14,Fstaff hold a graduate teaching
OL,15,Fqualification, according to the DfE.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,FSarah Ronan, director of the Early
OL,7,FEducation and Childcare Coalition,
OL,8,Fsaid attracting more graduates into
OL,9,Fthe sector will have a "positive
OL,10,Fimpact" on nursery children and
OL,11,Fwelcomed the government's announcement
OL,12,Fon Tuesday.
OL,14,F"When disadvantaged children start
OL,15,Fschool 4.7 months behind their better-
OL,16,Foff peers, it's right that we do
OL,17,Feverything we can to close that gap as
OL,18,Fearly as possible," she said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781024765
OL,3,CNursery teachers in deprived areas to
OL,4,Cbe offered #4,500 bonus
OL,6,F"Research shows us that graduate
OL,7,Fteachers can have a positive impact on
OL,8,Fchild development, particularly for
OL,9,Fthose at risk of being left behind.
OL,11,F"We welcome this incentive to attract
OL,12,Fmore graduates to work in communities
OL,13,Fwhere they can make a difference and
OL,14,Fchange lives."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
